    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704170/extras/defc770e4463f627620b278aa4c490f7.poster.avif?t=1757584579\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704170/extras/defc770e4463f627620b278aa4c490f7.webm?t=1757584579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704170/extras/defc770e4463f627620b278aa4c490f7.mp4?t=1757584579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Armor. Chaos. Total Destruction.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into high‑octane tank combat where every wall is just a temporary inconvenience. Everything you see on the map can be reduced to rubble. No artificial barriers—only you, your rivals, and a battlefield that disappears under treads and heavy fire.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704170/extras/005f55b36bafe92946ac1d3dd249f6f3.poster.avif?t=1757584579\" width=780 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704170/extras/005f55b36bafe92946ac1d3dd249f6f3.webm?t=1757584579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704170/extras/005f55b36bafe92946ac1d3dd249f6f3.mp4?t=1757584579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Why You’ll Love It</i></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Online PvP With Friends:</strong> Squad up or face off in intense, fast‑paced tank battles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Power‑Ups &amp; Progression:</strong> Grab airborne drops or earn rewards mid‑match to boost armor, firepower, reload speed, mobility, and restore HP.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level Up &amp; Unlock:</strong> Score big, unlock new stages, upgrade your tank, and carve your legend into the battlefield.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fully Destructible Environments:</strong> Blast through buildings, defenses, and anything in your way—create your own attack paths.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704170/extras/2a0e79ba7b85cb22e1594f1adc51baee.poster.avif?t=1757584579\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704170/extras/2a0e79ba7b85cb22e1594f1adc51baee.webm?t=1757584579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704170/extras/2a0e79ba7b85cb22e1594f1adc51baee.mp4?t=1757584579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Modes</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🛑 Survival</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate a mine‑strewn battlefield packed with unique challenges and special rewards. Complete objectives, dodge traps, earn points—every move is a risk that could pay off huge… or end in a spectacular explosion.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🤝 Co‑Op</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up against AI forces. Capture and hold territory, build walls and traps, coordinate maneuvers. In this mode, teamwork is everything—and the map rewards squads that think ahead.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔥 Classic Multiplayer: Free‑For‑All</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No rules. No mercy. Rack up points by destroying anyone who crosses your sightline. Play online with friends—today’s ally can be tomorrow’s target.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Living, Hazard‑Filled Battlefield</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Missile turrets.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explosive walls.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden surprises you’ll only discover in combat.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every map tests your reflexes, strategy, and nerve.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Airdrops Change Everything</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch the skies: when a cargo plane appears, it’s carrying rare loot. Reach the drop before your enemies to secure strategic upgrades—reinforcements, repairs, limited‑time boosts, and more.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ready?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fire up the engine, rally your crew, level the map, and prove whose tank rules the warzone. Your tactics. Your tracks. Your victory.</p>",
